title: It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia
fullTitle: It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia (TV Series 2005â€“ )

episodes.title: The Gang Gets Romantic
episodes.plot: Mac concocts a scheme to attract single women to rent Dennis's bedroom while Frank and Charlie make similar plans to draw in young European coeds, but neither ad attracts their intended target.

episodes.title: Thunder Gun 4: Maximum Cool
episodes.plot: The Gang finds themselves in the middle of a focus group after a screening of Thunder Gun 4: Maximum Cool.

episodes.title: Dee Day
episodes.plot: The guys are in the final preparation stage for an unknown scheme when Dee excitedly enters to inform them that today is "Dee Day" and the guys must do everything she wants without complaint.

episodes.title: The Gang Chokes
episodes.plot: Annoyed that the Gang failed to react as he nearly choked to death on an appetizer, Frank decides the Waiter, his savior, is the only person who has his back.

episodes.title: The Gang Texts
episodes.plot: During their trip to the Philadelphia Zoo, Mac sets up a group text for The Gang that leads to confusion.

episodes.title: The Janitor Always Mops Twice
episodes.plot: In the black-and-white noir world of his memory, Charlie navigates the seedy underbelly of Philadelphia as Frank has been "diarrhea poisoned," and it's up to Charlie to clean up the mess.

episodes.title: The Gang Solves Global Warming
episodes.plot: As a record-breaking heat wave overtakes Philly, the Gang plans to profit from global warming by pumping up the A/C so people will congregate at Paddy's and save energy at home.

episodes.title: Paddy's Has a Jumper
episodes.plot: While a suicidal man threatens to jump off Paddy's pub, the gang wonders whether they should help the poor man or let him fall to his death.

episodes.title: A Woman's Right to Chop
episodes.plot: When a trendy new hair salon opens up right next door to Paddy's, Dennis and Frank go on the offensive to stop women from cutting off their hair. Meanwhile, Mac is reunited with his childhood dog Poppins.

episodes.title: Waiting for Big Mo
episodes.plot: Dennis and Charlie stand guard at the entrance to their laser tag base waiting to ambush the legendary "Big Mo," but Dennis begins to ponder the reasons they play laser tag and if their pursuit of a victory is worth their effort.
